page.content: {Shawbury}is made up of{modern}housing estates. The most popular type of housing is {semi_detached}housing.188 out of 420 homes are semi_detached.123 out of 420 homes are{detached.} There are 21{bungalows}and 52{ {terraced}houses.Some old people live in{flats}and there are 16 of these in 3 blocks.Two families live in{ {caravans. { }The most popular number of{bedrooms in a house is{3.116}out of{420}homes have 3 bedrooms.The largest number of bedrooms is 7.Only one house has 7 bedrooms.67 homes have 2 bedrooms,23 have 4,6 have 1 bedroom and 2 have 5 bedrooms. There are a few homes scattered around our area and these are mainly{ {farmhouses. { }
